---
// src/components/About.astro
---
<section class="about container" id="about">
  <p class="section-label">about</p>
  <div class="content">
    <p>
      I'm a backend engineer who builds the systems that power what users never see —
      clean APIs, reliable data pipelines, and business logic that scales. I work
      primarily with Ruby on Rails and GraphQL, currently shipping production features
      at AgrigateOne where I design and maintain a monolith API serving agricultural
      logistics across shipments, finance, and yield tracking.
    </p>
    <p>
      I care about writing code that's easy to understand and hard to break.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md);
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 640px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  p + p { color: var(--color-muted); }
</style>
